. * Panel (b): Procurement vs non-procurement firms (base spec)
. *-----------------------------------------------------------------------
. 
. preserve

. collapse (mean) mu_pp=mu_A [aw=w_cost], by(year pp_dummy)

. 
. reshape wide mu_pp, i(year) j(pp_dummy)
(j = 0 1)

